<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SHEIN - Avaliar Look</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="app" aria-label="Avaliação de look SHEIN">
      <header class="brand-bar">
        <svg
          class="brand-logo"
          height="30"
          viewBox="0 0 105.783 22"
          width="150"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          aria-label="SHEIN"
          role="img"
        >
          <path
            d="M16.5 15.95c0 .825-.183 1.558-.55 2.2-.367.733-.917 1.283-1.558 1.833a6.62 6.62 0 0 1-2.384 1.284c-.916.275-1.925.458-3.025.458-1.008 0-1.925-.092-2.658-.183-.825-.092-1.558-.275-2.292-.459-.733-.183-1.375-.55-2.016-.825-.642-.366-1.284-.825-2.017-1.283l3.208-2.842c.917.734 1.834 1.192 2.75 1.467.917.275 1.834.458 2.842.458.458 0 .825-.091 1.192-.183A3.39 3.39 0 0 0 11 17.417c.275-.184.458-.459.642-.642.183-.275.275-.55.275-.825 0-.367-.092-.642-.184-.917-.091-.275-.366-.55-.733-.733-.367-.275-.825-.458-1.467-.733a17.513 17.513 0 0 0-2.383-.825c-.825-.275-1.65-.55-2.475-.917S3.208 11 2.658 10.542c-.55-.459-1.1-1.1-1.375-1.742C.825 7.975.642 7.15.642 6.233c0-.916.183-1.741.55-2.475.366-.733.916-1.375 1.65-1.925.641-.458 1.466-.916 2.383-1.191S7.15.183 8.158.183c1.742 0 3.3.184 4.492.642 1.192.458 2.292 1.008 3.208 1.833L12.742 5.5c-.55-.458-1.192-.917-1.925-1.192-.734-.275-1.559-.366-2.475-.366-.459 0-.825.091-1.192.183-.458.092-.733.275-1.008.458-.275.184-.459.459-.642.734s-.275.55-.275.825c0 .366.092.641.275.916.092.275.367.459.733.734.367.275.825.458 1.467.733s1.375.55 2.292.825c1.191.367 2.108.733 2.933 1.192.825.458 1.467.916 2.017 1.466s.916 1.1 1.191 1.742.367 1.375.367 2.2zm25.758 5.5h-4.491v-9.167h-8.342v9.167h-4.492V.642h4.492v8.25h8.342V.642h4.491zm24.842 0H50.692V.642H67.1v3.3H55.092v4.95h11.091V12.1H55.092v5.683H67.1zm13.292 0H75.9V.642h4.492zM105.783.642V22L93.225 11.092v10.175h-4.4V0l12.558 10.908V.642z"
          />
        </svg>
      </header>

      <section class="content" id="evaluation-view">
        <div class="balance-pill" aria-label="Saldo disponível">
          <span class="coin" aria-hidden="true">💰</span>
          <strong id="balance-brl">R$ --,--</strong>
          <span class="usd" id="balance-usd">($30.00)</span>
          <span class="label">saldo</span>
        </div>

        <p class="step" id="look-step">LOOK 1 DE 6</p>
        <p class="reward" id="look-reward">
          +<span id="reward-brl">R$ --,--</span>
          <span id="reward-usd">($8.50)</span> por evaluar esta prenda
        </p>

        <figure class="look-card">
          <img
            id="look-image"
            src="assets/look-1.webp"
            alt="Look 1 com conjunto branco em frente ao espelho"
          />
        </figure>

        <div class="answers" role="group" aria-label="Escolha sua avaliação">
          <button type="button" class="answer" data-value="love">
            <span aria-hidden="true">😍</span>
            La usaría sin dudar
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="answer" data-value="change">
            <span aria-hidden="true">😊</span>
            Me gustó, pero cambiaría algo
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="answer" data-value="ok">
            <span aria-hidden="true">😐</span>
            Está bien, nada especial
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="answer" data-value="style">
            <span aria-hidden="true">🤔</span>
            No es mi estilo
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="answer" data-value="no">
            <span aria-hidden="true">❌</span>
            No la usaría
          </button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="summary-view" id="summary-view" hidden>
        <div class="balance-pill summary-pill" aria-label="Saldo disponível">
          <span class="coin" aria-hidden="true">💰</span>
          <strong id="summary-pill-brl">R$ --,--</strong>
          <span class="usd" id="summary-pill-usd">($76.50)</span>
          <span class="label">saldo</span>
        </div>

        <div class="summary-hero-icon" aria-hidden="true">💰</div>
        <h2 class="summary-title">¡Evaluación completa!</h2>
        <p class="summary-copy">
          Ganaste dinero por cada prenda que evaluaste. Tu opinión ayuda a Shein
          a decidir qué producir.
        </p>

        <div class="summary-total">
          <strong id="summary-total-brl">R$ --,--</strong>
          <span id="summary-total-usd">≈ $76.50 USD</span>
        </div>

        <section class="earnings-box" aria-labelledby="earnings-title">
          <h3 id="earnings-title">RESUMEN DE GANANCIAS</h3>

          <div class="earnings-row">
            <span>Saldo inicial</span>
            <span>
              <strong id="summary-start-brl">R$ --,--</strong>
              <span id="summary-start-usd">($30.00)</span>
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="earnings-row">
            <span>Ganado evaluando</span>
            <span class="positive">
              <strong id="summary-earned-brl">+R$ --,--</strong>
              <span id="summary-earned-usd">($46.50)</span>
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="earnings-divider"></div>

          <div class="earnings-row total-row">
            <span>Saldo total</span>
            <span>
              <strong id="summary-box-total-brl">R$ --,--</strong>
              <span id="summary-box-total-usd">$76.50</span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="summary-list" id="summary-list" aria-label="Looks avaliados"></div>

        <button class="withdraw-button" type="button">RETIRAR MI DINERO</button>
      </section>
    </main>

    <div class="reward-modal" id="reward-modal" hidden>
      <div class="reward-dialog" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="reward-title">
        <button class="modal-close" id="modal-close" type="button" aria-label="Fechar popup">
          ×
        </button>

        <img
          class="modal-look"
          id="modal-look-image"
          src="assets/look-1.png"
          alt="Look avaliado"
        />

        <div class="modal-balance" aria-label="Saldo atualizado">
          <span class="coin" aria-hidden="true">💰</span>
          <strong id="modal-balance-brl">R$ --,--</strong>
          <span id="modal-balance-usd">($30.00)</span>
          <span class="label">saldo</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="modal-added" id="reward-title">
          +<span id="modal-reward-brl">R$ --,--</span>
          <span id="modal-reward-usd">($8.50)</span> agregados
          <span aria-hidden="true">💰</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="modal-copy">
          ¡Gracias por tu opinión! El dinero fue sumado a tu saldo. Seguí evaluando
          para ganar más.
        </p>

        <button class="modal-action" id="modal-action" type="button">
          CONTINUAR EVALUANDO
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <audio id="cash-sound" src="assets/cash-register.mp3" preload="auto"></audio>
    <script src="script.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
